1. If current time = 7:00 AM → turn ON lights and open curtains  
2. If current time = 11:00 PM → turn OFF all lights and close curtains  
3. If room temperature > 30°C → turn ON air conditioner  
4. If room temperature < 20°C → turn ON heater  
5. If room temperature between 20°C and 30°C → turn OFF both AC and heater  
6. Auto Mode can be toggled ON/OFF from Dashboard
